12
) toes lacking lateral fringes; basal webbing absent; Toe V slightly longer in length than Toe III; toe tips round, bulbous, lacking discs; (
13
) in life, dorsum brownish-black with few scattered white to yellow spots, venter dark brown with irregular diffuse white to gray blotches; (
